Reasoning: The paper proposes a new pulse position modulation scheme for communication systems, specifically for peak power limited systems such as impulse radio ultra wide band systems and free space optical communications. This falls under the sub-categories of information theory (cs.IT), communication and networking (cs.COMM), signal processing (cs.SI), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), and physics and society (cs.PHY).
